OL,3,CThe terrifying moment boy clings to
OL,4,Cback of moving bus
OL,6,FA woman has captured the terrifying
OL,7,Fmoment a young boy was seen clinging
OL,8,Fto the back of a moving Bee Network
OL,9,Fbus in Salford.
OL,11,FThe incident happened at the Cromwell
OL,12,FRoad roundabout in Pendleton on
OL,13,FTuesday afternoon (October 31).
OL,14,FFootage taken by a passing driver
OL,15,Fshows the boy hanging onto the rear of
OL,16,Fthe bus as it moved off, before
OL,17,Fjumping down moments later at the next
OL,18,Fstop.
