OL,3,CThe terrifying moment boy clings to
OL,4,Cback of moving bus
OL,6,FThe witness, who shared the video,
OL,7,Fsaid she began filming after seeing
OL,8,Fthe boy slip before managing to grab
OL,9,Fonto the vehicle.
OL,11,F"There were two lads and the first one
OL,12,FI caught getting on the back of a bus
OL,13,Fand the second one ran and jumped on
OL,14,Fthe bus in front of them." She said.
OL,16,F"He slipped at first and my heart
OL,17,Fabsolutely sank, I thought I was going
OL,18,Fto be sick.
