OL,3,CThe terrifying moment boy clings to
OL,4,Cback of moving bus
OL,6,F"There was a car right behind the bus,
OL,7,FI thought, he fell off he's going to
OL,8,Fget run over. He hung on for dear life.
OL,10,F"Last week I saw it twice around
OL,11,FSalford Precinct and nearly every day
OL,12,Fthis week. It's all on the 52 and
OL,13,Fnumber 10 bus route."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Transport for
OL,16,FGreater Manchester (TfGM) said the
OL,17,Fbehaviour was "incredibly dangerous"
OL,18,Fand could have "tragic consequences."
