OL,3,CThe terrifying moment boy clings to
OL,4,Cback of moving bus
OL,6,F"This is another example of young
OL,7,Fpeople completely ignoring the risks
OL,8,Fthat come with this kind of
OL,9,Fbehaviour," the spokesperson said.
OL,10,F"It's not only a criminal offence, but
OL,11,Fit could result in serious injury or
OL,12,Fworse. Parents and guardians need to
OL,13,Ftalk to their children about the risks
OL,14,Fand ask them if it's really worth it."
OL,16,FIt comes just weeks after similar
OL,17,Ffootage emerged showing two boys
OL,18,Fclinging to the back of a 52 service
OL,19,Ftravelling from Failsworth to Trafford.
